    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the CFD hemolysis model supporting the CPB use case is accepted. Seven of thirteen factors were assessed and all assessed factors met or exceeded their required credibility levels for MRL 2. The remaining six factors were determined not-assessed or scoped out in accordance with the MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The model is considered sufficiently credible to support the intended regulatory submission decision.",
